== 製作 ==
=== 發展 ===
2009年2月，[[華納兄弟|華納兄弟公司]]宣布聘請賈斯汀·馬克斯來為《自殺小隊》編劇，並由[[林暐|林暐]]和[[查爾斯·羅文|查爾斯·羅文]]擔任監製、{{link-en|柯林·威爾森|Colin Wilson (film producer)}}作為執行製片人<ref>{{cite news|last1=Caranicas|first1=Peter|title=Below the Line Bookings|url=http://variety.com/2014/artisans/news/below-the-line-bookings-7-1201319626/|accessdate=2014-10-03|work=[[Variety_(magazine)|Variety]]|date=2014-10-02|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20141007124310/http://variety.com/2014/artisans/news/below-the-line-bookings-7-1201319626/|archivedate=2014-10-07}}</ref><ref name="OctoberDeadline" /><ref>{{cite web |author=Dave McNary |url=http://variety.com/2009/film/news/warner-bros-sets-up-suicide-squad-1118000590/ |title=Warner Bros. sets up ‘Suicide Squad’ |publisher=Variety |date=2009-02-25 |accessdate=2015-05-17 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150703210106/http://variety.com/2009/film/news/warner-bros-sets-up-suicide-squad-1118000590/ |archivedate=2015-07-03 }}</ref>。2014年9月，[[大衛·艾亞|大衛·艾亞]]被任命擔任導演和編劇<ref>{{cite news|title=Warner Bros. Circling David Ayer for DC Comics’ ‘Suicide Squad’ (Exclusive)|url=http://variety.com/2014/film/news/warner-bros-circling-david-ayer-for-adaptation-of-dc-comics-suicide-squad-1201308883/|accessdate=2014-09-19|work=[[Variety_(magazine)|Variety]]|date=2014-09-19|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140921004240/http://variety.com/2014/film/news/warner-bros-circling-david-ayer-for-adaptation-of-dc-comics-suicide-squad-1201308883/|archivedate=2014-09-21}}</ref><ref>Kit, Borys. [http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/scribe-suicide-squad-pact-79891 "Scribe In for 'Suicide Squad' Pact"] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150924201500/http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/scribe-suicide-squad-pact-79891 |date=2015-09-24 }}. ''[[The_Hollywood_Reporter|The Hollywood Reporter]]''. February 25, 2009.</ref>。而[[查爾斯·羅文|查爾斯·羅文]]也將參與製片<ref name="OctoberDeadline" />。2014年10月20日，艾亞於《[[帝國雜誌|帝國雜誌]]》談論了關於電影，他說：「這會是《[[決死突擊隊|決死突擊隊]]》的壞蛋版本」<ref>{{cite news|last1=de Semlyen|first1=Phil|title=David Ayer Talks DC’s Suicide Squad|url=http://www.empireonline.com/news/story.asp?NID=42521|accessdate=2014-10-21|work=Empire|date=2014-10-20|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20141022211037/http://www.empireonline.com/news/story.asp?NID=42521|archivedate=2014-10-22}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://screenrant.com/david-ayer-suicide-squad-comic-book-source-material-harley-quinn/ |title=David Ayer Teases ‘Suicide Squad’ Comic Book Influences, Harley Quinn’s Motivation |publisher=Screenrant.com |date= |accessdate=2015-05-17 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150502062158/http://screenrant.com/david-ayer-suicide-squad-comic-book-source-material-harley-quinn/ |archivedate=2015-05-02 }}</ref>。2015年3月28日，艾亞戲弄說，這部電影也將擁有DC的[[阿卡漢精神病院|阿卡漢精神病院]]，自殺小隊的家庭成員包括[[死亡射手|死亡射手]]、重磅炸彈、毒藤女、哈莉·奎茵和小丑<ref>{{cite news|last1=Perry|first1=Spencer|title=Suicide Squad Director David Ayer Teases a Trip to Arkham Asylum|url=http://www.comingsoon.net/movies/news/424047-suicide-squad-director-david-ayer-teases-a-trip-to-arkham-asylum|accessdate=2015-03-29|publisher=comingsoon.net|date=2015-03-28|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150330173042/http://www.comingsoon.net/movies/news/424047-suicide-squad-director-david-ayer-teases-a-trip-to-arkham-asylum|archivedate=2015-03-30}}</ref>。

=== 選角 ===
