1-07|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20141109103232/http://www.thewrap.com/jared-leto-eyed-to-play-the-joker-in-wbs-suicide-squad-exclusive/|archivedate=2014-11-09}}</ref>。由於雷托在《[[藥命俱樂部|藥命俱樂部]]》之後還未有其他片約，因此他接下此角的機會較大<ref name="LetoCast" />。11月9日，宣布[[瑪格·羅比|瑪格·羅比]]將飾演小丑的女友[[哈莉·奎茵|哈莉·奎茵]]<ref name=RobbieCast>{{cite news|last1=Goldberg|first1=Matt|title=Margot Robbie to Play Harley Quinn in SUICIDE SQUAD|url=http://collider.com/harley-quinn-suicide-squad-movie-margot-robbie/|accessdate=2014-11-10|publisher=Collider|date=2014-11-09|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20141110070459/http://collider.com/harley-quinn-suicide-squad-movie-margot-robbie/|archivedate=2014-11-10}}</ref>。11月12日，據傳[[威爾·史密斯|威爾·史密斯]]將會飾演[[蝙蝠俠|蝙蝠俠]]的敵人[[死亡射手|死射]]<ref name=CourtneyVariety>{{cite news|last1=Kroll|first1=Justin|title=Jai Courtney Eyed for Batman Villain Deadshot in ‘Suicide Squad’|url=http://variety.com/2014/film/news/jai-courtney-eyed-for-batman-villain-deadshot-in-suicide-squad-exclusive-1201354892/|accessdate=2014-11-13|work=[[Variety_(magazine)|Variety]]|date=2014-11-12|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20141114052530/http://variety.com/2014/film/news/jai-courtney-eyed-for-batman-villain-deadshot-in-suicide-squad-exclusive-1201354892/|archivedate=2014-11-14}}</ref>。而哈迪似乎則在談判團隊的創始成員之一{{link-en|瑞克·弗拉格|Rick Flag}}，但也有消息人士透露是[[閃電俠|閃電俠]]的敵人[[迴旋鏢隊長|迴旋鏢隊長]]<ref name="CourtneyVariety" />。2014年12月2日，官方證實，史密斯、哈迪、雷托、羅比、[[傑·寇特尼|傑·寇特尼]]和[[卡拉·迪樂芬妮|卡拉·迪樂芬妮]]全已簽署了片約，他們分別飾演[[死亡射手|死射]]、{{link-en|瑞克·弗萊格|Rick Flag}}、[[小丑_(漫畫)|小丑]]、[[哈莉·奎茵|哈莉·奎茵]]、[[迴旋鏢隊長|迴旋鏢隊長]]與{{link-en|魅惑女巫 (DC漫畫)|Enchantress (DC Comics)|魅惑女巫}}<ref name=DecemberConfirmed>{{cite news|last1=Sneider|first1=Jeff|title=Will Smith, Tom Hardy, Jared Leto, Margot Robbie Set for ‘Suicide Squad’|url=http://www.thewrap.com/will-smith-tom-hardy-jared-leto-margot-robbie-set-for-suicide-squad/|accessdate=2015-02-19|publisher=thewrap.com|date=2014-12-02|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150219102802/http://www.thewrap.com/will-smith-tom-hardy-jared-leto-margot-robbie-set-for-suicide-squad/|archivedate=2015-02-19}}</ref>。艾森伯格則還在進行談判，此外工作室也在尋求一位中年非洲裔的女演員來飾演[[阿曼達·華勒|阿曼達·華勒]]，便此鎖定了[[薇拉·戴維絲|薇拉·戴維絲]]、[[奧塔薇亞·史班森|奧塔薇亞·史班森]]和[[歐普拉·溫芙蕾|歐普拉·溫芙蕾]]<ref>{{cite news|last1=Kroll|first1=Justin|title=‘Suicide Squad’ Cast Revealed: Jared Leto to Play the Joker, Will Smith is Deadshot|url=http://variety.com/2014/film/news/suicide-squad-cast-revealed-jared-leto-to-play-the-joker-will-smith-is-deadshot-1201368867/|accessdate=2015-02-19|publisher=variety.com|date=2014-12-02|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150626125327/http://variety.com/2014/film/news/suicide-squad-cast-revealed-jared-leto-to-play-the-joker-will-smith-is-deadshot-1201368867/|archivedate=2015-06-26}}</ref>。漫畫書作者{{link-en|約翰·奧斯特蘭德|John Ostrander}}與{{link-en|Comic Book Resources|Comic Book Resources}}談到關於選角，他說：「我認為選角沒有什麼問題...。我真的對這選角感到印象深刻，他們得到了些很不錯的演員來詮釋這些角色」<ref>{{cite news|title="Suicide Squad" Creator Weighs In on Film Casting, Concept|url=http://www.comicbookresources.com/?page=article&id=57562|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20141231202915/http://www.comicbookresources.com/?page=article&id=57562|archivedate=2014-12-31|accessdate=2014-12-09|publisher=Comic Book Resources|date=2014-12-05|deadurl=yes}}</ref>。

後來在2015年1月初，[[薇拉·戴維絲|薇拉·戴維絲]]在採訪中表示，她很感興趣詮釋[[阿曼達·華勒|阿曼達·華勒]]，說：「我迷上了她（華勒）」<ref>{{cite news|last1=Topel|first1=Fred|title=Viola Davis Talks Amanda Waller in ‘Suicide Squad’|url=http://www.nerdreport.com/2015/01/07/viola-davis-talks-amanda-waller-suicide-squad/|accessdate=2015-02-19|publisher=nerdreport.com|date=2015-01-07|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150212034000/http://www.nerdreport.com/2015/01/07/viola-davis-talks-amanda-waller-suicide-squad/|archivedate=2015-02-12}}</ref>。後來，湯姆·哈迪因故離開了電影，工作室洽談了[[傑克·葛倫霍|傑克·葛倫霍]]來頂替，但被拒絕。而[[喬爾·埃哲頓|喬爾·埃哲頓]]、[[強·柏恩瑟|強·柏恩瑟]]或[[喬爾·金納曼|喬爾·金納曼]]有望取代哈迪飾演瑞克·弗拉格<ref>{{cite web|url=http://variety.com/2015/film/news/jake-gyllenhaal-suicide-squad-rick-flag-1201411414/|title=Jake Gyllenhaal Passes on ‘Suicide Squad’|work=Collider|accessdate=2015-01-21|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150122062446/http://variety.com/2015/film/news/jake-gyllenhaal-suicide-squad-rick-flag-1201411414/|archivedate=2015-01-22}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.cineblend.com/news/Suicide-Squad-Wants-To-Replace-Tom-Hardy-With-One-Two-Actors-69|title=Suicide Squad Wants To Replace Tom Hardy With One Of These Two Actors|publisher=CinemaBlend|last=O'Connell|first=Sean|date=2015-01-22}}{{Dead link|date=2019年5月 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}</ref><ref name=KinnamanTalks>{{cite web|url=http://www.thewrap.com/joel-kinnaman-eyed-to-replace-tom-hardy-in-wbs-suicide-squad/|title=Joel Kinnaman to Replace Tom Hardy as Rick Flagg in WB's 'Suicide Squad'|publisher=The Wrap|last1=Sneider|first1=Jeff|last2=Ge|first2=Linda|date=2015-02-13|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150709125536/http://www.thewrap.com/joel-kinnaman-eyed-to-replace-tom-hardy-in-wbs-suicide-squad/|archivedate=2015-07-09}}</ref>。2月18日，TheWrap證實[[傑·赫南德茲|傑·赫南德茲]]加入劇組飾演未知角色和金納曼將飾演瑞克<ref name=HernandezKinnamanCast>{{cite news|last1=Sneider|first1=Jeff|title=Jay Hernandez Joining Will Smith, Jared Leto in WB’s ‘Suicide Squad’ (Exclusive)|url=http://www.thewrap.com/jay-hernandez-joining-will-smith-jared-leto-in-wbs-suicide-squad-exclusive/|accessdate=2015-02-19|publisher=thewrap.com|date=2015-02-18|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150219065922/http://www.thewrap.com/jay-hernandez-joining-will-smith-jared-leto-in-wbs-suicide-squad-exclusive/|archivedate=2015-02-19}}</ref>。2015年2月，《[[告示牌_(雜誌)|告示牌]]》表示，雷托的小丑被稱為「莎士比亞般的角色」<ref>{{cite news|last1=Lynch|first1=Joe|title=Billboard Cover Sneak Peek: Jared Leto Talks Gaining Weight to Play the Joker in 'Suicide Squad'|url=http://www.billboard.com/articles/news/6479914/jared-leto-gaining-weight-playing-joker-suicide-squad?mobile_redirection=false|accessdate=2015-02-21|publisher=billboard.com|date=2015-02-19|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150223113147/http://www.billboard.com/articles/news/6479914/jared-leto-gaining-weight-playing-joker-suicide-squad?mobile_redirection=false|archivedate=2015-02-23}}</ref>。在[[第87屆奧斯卡金像獎|第87屆奧斯卡金像獎]]紅毯上，[[CTV電視網|CTV電視網]]的《{{link-en|etalk|etalk}}》主持人{{link-en|班·馬爾羅尼|Ben Mulroney}}證實了戴維絲將飾演亞曼達·華勒<ref name=DavisCast>{{cite web|title=Davis confirms her role to etalk's Ben Mulroney|url=https://twitter.com/etalkCTV/status/570296573751648256|publisher=twitter.com|accessdate=2015-03-02|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150226083512/https://twitter.com/etalkctv/status/570296573751648256|archivedate=2015-02-26}}</ref>。2015年2月28日，導演艾亞在自己的Twitter上描述小丑一角是「莊嚴的」<ref>{{cite web|title=Ayer about Leto's Joker on Twitter|url=https://twitter.com/DavidAyerMovies/status/571700425008799745|publisher=twitter.com|accessdate=2015-03-02|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150309235023/https://twitter.com/DavidAyerMovies/status/571700425008799745|archivedate=2015-03-09}}</ref>。《{{link-en|多倫多太陽報|Toronto Sun}}》在2015年3月26日證實了拳擊手兼演員的雷蒙德·歐盧博威爾將飾演未知的角色<ref name=OlubowaleCast>{{cite web|last1=Buffery|first1=Steve|title=Olubowale's back and ready to rumble with Ruddock|url=http://www.torontosun.com/2015/03/26/olubowales-back-and-ready-to-rumble-with-ruddock|website=Toronto Sun|accessdate=2015-03-30|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150402104902/http://www.torontosun.com/2015/03/26/olubowales-back-and-ready-to-rumble-with-ruddock|archivedate=2015-04-02}}</ref>。2015年3月29日，[[史考特·伊斯威特|史考特·伊斯威特]]在Twitter上表明了自己將參演本片<ref name=EastwoodCast>{{cite web|title=#Breaking - @ScottEastwood confirms to #etalk he's been in Toronto working on #SuicideSquad. More to come tomorrow.|url=https://twitter.com/etalkCTV/status/582213320326926336|website=Twitter|publisher=ETalk|date=2015-03-29|accessdate=2015-03-30|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150331003114/https://twitter.com/etalkCTV/status/582213320326926336|archivedate=2015-03-31}}</ref>。3月31日，[[艾德瓦利·亞肯努耶-阿嘉巴傑|艾德瓦利·亞肯努耶-阿嘉巴傑]]將飾演[[殺手鱷|殺手鱷]]，TheWrap證實日本裔美國女演員[[福原凱倫|福原凱倫]]也將出演未知的角色<ref name="AgbajeCast">{{cite web |url=http://www.thewrap.com/adewale-akinnuoye-agbaje-to-play-killer-croc-in-wbs-suicide-squad-exclusive/ |title=Adewale Akinnuoye-Agbaje to Play Killer Croc in WB’s ‘Suicide Squad’ (Exclusive) |publisher=TheWrap |date=2015-03-31 |accessdate=2015-03-31 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160625160643/http://www.thewrap.com/adewale-akinnuoye-agbaje-to-play-killer-croc-in-wbs-suicide-squad-exclusive/ |archivedate=2016-06-25 }}</ref>。後來，Latino-Review網站指出她將飾演原作中重要角色{{link-en|塑料炸彈|Plastique (comics)}}<ref name=FukuharaCast>{{cite news|last1=Mayimbe|first1=El|title=Adewale Akinnuoye-Agbaje To Play Killer Croc; Karen Fukuhara Rumored For Plastique In 'Suicide Squad'|url=http://www.latino-review.com/news/adewale-akinnuoye-agbaje-to-play-killer-croc-karen-fukuhara-rumored-for-plastique-in-suicide-squad|accessdate=2015-04-01|publisher=latino-review.com|date=2015-03-31|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150414070356/http://www.latino-review.com/news/adewale-akinnuoye-agbaje-to-play-killer-croc-karen-fukuhara-rumored-for-plastique-in-suicide-squad|archivedate=2015-04-14}}</ref>。但後來官方透露是飾演卡塔娜。另外三個劇組成員被揭露於2015年4月8日，包括{{link-en|亞當·畢奇|Adam Beach}}、[[艾克·拜瑞豪茲|艾克·拜瑞豪茲]]與[[吉姆·派瑞克|吉姆·派瑞克]]<ref name=AdditionalCast>{{cite news|title=‘Suicide Squad': First Cast Photo Revealed|url=http://variety.com/2015/film/news/suicide-squad-first-cast-photo-revealed-1201468975/|accessdate=2015-04-09|work=variety.com|date=2015-04-08|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150626105028/http://variety.com/2015/film/news/suicide-squad-first-cast-photo-revealed-1201468975/|archivedate=2015-06-26}}</ref>。2016年1月，[[班·艾佛列克|班·艾佛列克]]證實自己也參演了[[蝙蝠俠|蝙蝠俠]]一角。

=== 拍攝 ===
[[File:Suicide_Squad_filming_in_Toronto_3.jpg|thumb]]
電影將從2015年4月中旬到2015年9月在位於[[加拿大|加拿大]][[安大略|安大略]]的[[多倫多|多倫多]]拍攝<ref>{{cite news|title=Suicide Squad Movie Starts Filming In Toronto In 2015, Jared Leto To Play Joker And Will Smith Is Captain Boomerang|url=http://www.kdramastars.com/articles/55002/20141120/suicide-squad-movie.htm|accessdate=2014-11-22|publisher=K Drama Stars|date=2014-11-20|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20141219010900/http://www.kdramastars.com/articles/55002/20141120/suicide-squad-movie.htm|archivedate=2014-12-19}}</ref>。2014年12月1日，《[[好萊塢報導|好萊塢報導]]》透露，{{link-en|松林多倫多工作室|Pinewood Toronto Studios}}已被預訂一空，將於2月中作前期準備<ref>{{cite news|last1=Vlessing|first1=Etan|title=David Ayer's 'Suicide Squad' to Shoot in Toronto For Warner Bros.|url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/heat-vision/david-ayers-suicide-squad-shoot-753015|accessdate=2014-12-02|work=[[The_Hollywood_Reporter|The Hollywood Reporter]]|date=2014-12-01|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20141202215526/http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/heat-vision/david-ayers-suicide-squad-shoot-753015|archivedate=2014-12-02}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|title=‘Suicide Squad’ set to begin filming in Toronto on April 15|url=http://www.onlocationvacations.com/2015/02/04/suicide-squad-set-to-begin-filming-in-toronto-on-april-15/|accessdate=2015-02-09|publisher=onlocationvacations.com|date=2015-02-04|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150208050016/http://www.onlocationvacations.com/2015/02/04/suicide-squad-set-to-begin-filming-in-toronto-on-april-15/|archivedate=2015-02-08}}</ref>。2015年2月，艾亞釋出一張照片，代表他們將開始製作道具<ref>{{cite news|last1=Outlaw|first1=Kofi|title=‘Suicide Squad’ Teaser Images: Hot Weapons, Big Set Pieces|url=http://screenrant.com/suicide-squad-movie-images-weapons/|accessdate=2015-03-08|publisher=screenrant.com|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150309235727/http://screenrant.com/suicide-squad-movie-images-weapons/|archivedate=2015-03-09}}</ref>。2015年3月初，又釋出照片，代表雷托正為自己的小丑角色剪髮<ref>{{cite news|last1=Comito|first1=BD|title=Jared Leto's Snapchat Shows He'll Make An Awesome Joker|url=http://comicbook.com/2015/03/05/jared-letos-snapchat-shows-hell-make-a-great-joker/|accessdate=2015-03-08|publisher=comicbook.com|date=2015-03-05|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150308162607/http://comicbook.com/2015/03/05/jared-letos-snapchat-shows-hell-make-a-great-joker|archivedate=2015-03-08}}</ref>。於{{link-en|加拿大導演協會|Directors Guild of Canada}}上證實，拍攝工作將於2015年4月13日開始至2015年8月30日期間進行<ref>{{cite news|title=Suicide Squad Will Officially Start Filming April 13th|url=http://dccomicsmovie.com/suicide-squad-will-officially-start-filming-april-13th/|accessdate=2015-04-08|work=dccomicsmovie.com|date=2015-03-27|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150403065651/http://dccomicsmovie.com/suicide-squad-will-officially-start-filming-april-13th/|archivedate=2015-04-03}}</ref>。於2015年4月13日正式宣布開拍<ref>{{cite news|title=David Ayer on Twitter|url=https://twitter.com/DavidAyerMovies/status/587710878100893696|accessdate=2015-04-13|work=Twitter|date=2015-04-13|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20151026034338/https://twitter.com/DavidAyerMovies/status/587710878100893696|archivedate=2015-10-26}}</ref>。4月26日和27日，計劃於Hy's Steakhouse拍攝<ref>{{cite news|title=‘Suicide Squad’ filming locations in Toronto on April 26 & 27|url=http://www.onlocationvacations.com/2015/04/24/suicide-squad-filming-locations-in-toronto-on-april-26-27/|accessdate=2015-04-26|work=onlocationvacations.com|date=2015-04-24|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150425231011/http://www.onlocationvacations.com/2015/04/24/suicide-squad-filming-locations-in-toronto-on-april-26-27/|archivedate=2015-04-25}}</ref>。其中一暴風雪的場景是於4月29日在阿得雷德和正里拍攝<ref>{{cite news|title=‘Suicide Squad’ is filming a “snowstorm” scene in Toronto tonight|url=http://www.onlocationvacations.com/2015/04/29/suicide-squad-is-filming-a-snowstorm-scene-in-toronto-tonight/#lightbox[gallery-86s0]/0/|accessdate=2015-05-02|work=onlocationvacations.com|date=2015-04-29|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150502035808/http://www.onlocationvacations.com/2015/04/29/suicide-squad-is-filming-a-snowstorm-scene-in-toronto-tonight/#lightbox|archivedate=2015-05-02}}</ref>。2015年5月5日的晚上，幾個主要場景是在多倫多的廣場市中心拍攝<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.news1130.com/2015/05/06/entertainment-city-suicide-squad/ |title=Entertainment City: 'Suicide Squad' |publisher=News1130 |date= |accessdate=2015-05-17 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150510063131/http://www.news1130.com/2015/05/06/entertainment-city-suicide-squad/ |archivedate=2015-05-10 }}</ref>。一個月後，被目擊到蝙蝠俠替身現身於片場<ref name=Batman-Filming>{{cite news|last1=Otterson|first1=Joe|title=‘Suicide Squad’ Set Leak Shows Ben Affleck’s Batman Hunting the Joker (Video)|url=http://www.thewrap.com/suicide-squad-set-leak-shows-ben-afflecks-batman-hunting-the-joker-video/|accessdate=2015-06-03|publisher=TheWrap|date=2015-05-28|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150531233202/http://www.thewrap.com/suicide-squad-set-leak-shows-ben-afflecks-batman-hunting-the-joker-video/|archivedate=2015-05-31}}</ref>。電影於2015年8月23日結束拍攝，接下來開始進入後製階段<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.comingsoon.net/movies/news/475391-production-wraps-on-suicide-squad-movie#/slide/1|title=Production Wraps on Suicide Squad Movie|work=ComingSoon.net|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20151117033708/http://www.comingsoon.net/movies/news/475391-production-wraps-on-suicide-squad-movie#/slide/1|archivedate=2015-11-17}}</ref>。據傳，2016年3月時還補拍了部分片段<ref>{{cite web |url=http://screenrant.com/suicide-squad-movie-reshoots/ |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2016-04-01 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160403133714/http://screenrant.com/suicide-squad-movie-reshoots/ |archivedate=2016-04-03 }}</ref>，但艾亞後來反駁了此傳言<ref>{{cite web |url=http://comicbook.com/2016/04/11/suicide-squad-director-says-reshoots-for-humor-rumor-is-silly/ |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2016-04-12 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160414151448/http://comicbook.com/2016/04/11/suicide-squad-director-says-reshoots-for-humor-rumor-is-silly |archivedate=2016-04-14 }}</ref>。

=== 音樂 ===
