2016年4月，英國奧斯卡獎得主作曲家[[史蒂文·普賴斯|史蒂文·普賴斯]]被宣布為電影作曲和配樂<ref>{{cite news|title=Behind The Scenes Look At Suicide Squad Scoring Session|url=https://comicbook.com/dc/2016/05/29/behind-the-scenes-look-at-suicide-squad-scoring-session/|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160530154324/http://comicbook.com/dc/2016/05/29/behind-the-scenes-look-at-suicide-squad-scoring-session/|archivedate=2016-05-30}}</ref>。電影原聲帶於2016年8月5日發行。

== 發行 ==
《自殺突擊隊》定於2016年8月5日上映<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.slashfilm.com/dc-movie-slate-revealed/|title=DC Comics Movies Announced: ‘Suicide Squad,’ ‘Wonder Woman,’ ‘Justice League,’ ‘The Flash,’ ‘Aquaman’|last=Fischer|first=Russ|publisher=/Film|date=2014-10-15|accessdate=2014-10-15|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6TQ91KdDF?url=http://www.slashfilm.com/dc-movie-slate-revealed/|archivedate=2014-10-18}}</ref>。在中國大陸電影圈則傳出該片未通過審查<ref>{{cite web|title='Suicide Squad' Unlikely to Get China Release|url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/heat-vision/suicide-squad-get-china-release-917206|publisher=The Hollywood Reporter|accessdate=2016-08-05|date=2016-08-04|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160806163002/http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/heat-vision/suicide-squad-get-china-release-917206|archivedate=2016-08-06}}</ref>，最終於2017年6月18日在[[上海国际电影节|上海国际电影节]]期間排片特映<ref>{{cite press release|url=http://www.siff.com/a/2017-06-06/1733.html|title=是时候燃一把!刺激你的神经 “成龙动作电影周”片单公布|publisher=[[上海国际电影节|上海国际电影节]]|via=|author=|language=|date=2017-06-06|accessdate=|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170808194032/http://www.siff.com/a/2017-06-06/1733.html|archivedate=2017-08-08|deadurl=no}}</ref>，未能公映。

=== 市場營銷 ===
劇組參加了[[聖地亞哥國際動漫展|2015年聖地亞哥國際動漫展]]，包括導演艾亞、演員[[威爾史密斯|史密斯]]、[[瑪格·羅比|羅比]]、[[傑·寇特尼|寇特尼]]、[[薇拉·戴維絲|戴維絲]]等人，並釋出了電影的首支預告片段。原本因為該預告被流出偷拍版，而使[[華納兄弟|華納兄弟]]和其反盜版團隊在過去48小時中不停地上網撤下側拍預告；但後來官方仍將正式清晰的預告放於網上，基於不想讓觀眾觀看畫質差的影片來影響本片的宣傳<ref>{{cite web|url=http://screenrant.com/suicide-squad-trailer-leak/|title='Suicide Squad': Warner Bros. Responds To Comic-Con Trailer Leak|work=Screen Rant|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150716145204/http://screenrant.com/suicide-squad-trailer-leak/|archivedate=2015-07-16}}</ref>。第二支預告於2016年1月19日隨[[CW電視網|CW電視網]]的DC特別節目釋出。

=== 家庭媒體 ===
電影的DVD與藍光於2016年11月15日發行，而加長版則於2016年12月13日推出，加長版中含有比正片多出13分鐘的片段<ref>{{cite web |url=https://twitter.com/SuicideSquadWB/status/783685958034034689 |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2016-10-24 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20161010110507/https://twitter.com/SuicideSquadWB/status/783685958034034689 |archivedate=2016-10-10 }}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/heat-vision/suicide-squad-extended-cut-be-935299|title='Suicide Squad' Extended Cut to Be Released After All|first=Aaron|last=Couch|work=[[The_Hollywood_Reporter|The Hollywood Reporter]]|date=2016-10-05|accessdate=2016-10-05|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20161006135832/http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/heat-vision/suicide-squad-extended-cut-be-935299|archivedate=2016-10-06}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.ign.com/articles/2016/10/05/suicide-squad-extended-cut-coming-to-blu-ray|title=SUICIDE SQUAD EXTENDED CUT COMING TO BLU-RAY|first=Nicole|last=Carpenter|work=[[IGN|IGN]]|date=2016-10-05|accessdate=2016-10-05|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20161006153224/http://www.ign.com/articles/2016/10/05/suicide-squad-extended-cut-coming-to-blu-ray|archivedate=2016-10-06}}</ref>。

== 迴響 ==

=== 評價 ===
《自殺特擊隊》獲得了整體負面的評價，[[爛番茄|爛番茄]]評價27%，基於387條評論，平均分為4.90/10<ref name="RT">{{cite web |url=https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/suicide_squad_2016/ |title=''Suicide Squad'' (2016) |work=[[Rotten_Tomatoes|Rotten Tomatoes]] |publisher=Fandango |accessdate=2016-09-15 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160914214209/https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/suicide_squad_2016/ |archivedate=2016-09-14 }}</ref>，在[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]上僅得到40分<ref name="Meta">{{cite web |url=http://www.metacritic.com/movie/suicide-squad |title=''Suicide Squad'' Reviews |work=[[Metacritic|Metacritic]] |publisher=[[CBS_Interactive|CBS Interactive]] |accessdate=2016-08-05 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160806112449/http://www.metacritic.com/movie/suicide-squad |archivedate=2016-08-06 }}</ref>，評價負面，多數好評傾向觀眾，專業評論主要批評場面過於混亂。與《[[蝙蝠俠對超人：正義曙光|正義曙光]]》一面倒的負面評價有些許差異。據[[CinemaScore|CinemaScore]]調查，觀眾的平均評價於A+至F間落於「B+」<ref>{{cite web|title=‘Suicide Squad’ Looking To Loot Year’s Third Biggest Opening With $140M-$145M|url=http://deadline.com/2016/08/suicide-squad-weekend-box-office-opening-will-smith-margot-robbie-1201799046/|first=Anthony|last=D'Alessandro|publisher=''Deadline''|date=2016-08-05|accessdate=2016-08-06|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160805215804/http://deadline.com/2016/08/suicide-squad-weekend-box-office-opening-will-smith-margot-robbie-1201799046/|archivedate=2016-08-05}}</ref>。

=== 票房 ===
在美國和加拿大，電影預計能從首映週末獲得1億至1.35億美元的票房，有望打破8月（此前為2014年的《[[星際異攻隊_(電影)|星際異攻隊]]》的9430萬美元）和[[威爾·史密斯|威爾·史密斯]]主演電影（此前為2007年的《[[我是傳奇|我是傳奇]]》的7720萬美元）的首映週末票房紀錄<ref name="preview">{{cite web|url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/heat-vision/box-office-suicide-squad-tracking-911029|title=Box Office: 'Suicide Squad' Tracking for Enormous $125M U.S. Debut|publisher=[[The_Hollywood_Reporter|The Hollywood Reporter]]|date=2016-07-14|accessdate=2016-07-14|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160715144623/http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/heat-vision/box-office-suicide-squad-tracking-911029|archivedate=2016-07-15}}</ref><ref name="preview2">{{cite web |url=http://deadline.com/2016/07/suicide-squad-will-smith-august-opening-box-office-record-1201786609/ |title=‘Suicide Squad’ Gunning For August & Will Smith Opening Records – Box Office |work=Deadline.com |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160715142436/http://deadline.com/2016/07/suicide-squad-will-smith-august-opening-box-office-record-1201786609/ |archivedate=2016-07-15 }}</ref>。美國首映週末票房高達1.3億美元，登上當週冠軍，而創下8月電影票房紀錄。上映三天，北美票房開出1.35億美元，海外票房則是1.32億美元，首週全球票房總計2.67億美元。由於本片預售票銷售頗佳，最終《自殺特擊隊》獲得了7.46億美元的全球票房，票房成績符合先前預期。

