2016年3月，[[華納兄弟|華納兄弟]]宣布，艾亞和史密斯將再次合作拍攝《[[光靈|光靈]]》和本片的續集<ref>{{cite web | url=http://www.thewrap.com/will-smith-joel-edgerton-to-star-in-david-ayers-cop-thriller-bright/ | title=Will Smith, Joel Edgerton to Star in David Ayer’s Cop Thriller ‘Bright’ | publisher=TheWrap | date=2016-03-02 | accessdate=2016-03-03 | last=Snider | first=Jeff | deadurl=no | archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160305122926/http://www.thewrap.com/will-smith-joel-edgerton-to-star-in-david-ayers-cop-thriller-bright/ | archivedate=2016-03-05 }}</ref><ref>{{cite web | date=2016-03-02 | first1=Justin | last1=Kroll | url=http://variety.com/2016/film/news/will-smith-david-ayer-bright-suicide-squad-1201696226/ | title=Will Smith, David Ayer Reteaming on Max Landis Spec ‘Bright’ | work=Variety | accessdate=2016-03-05 | deadurl=no | archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160929144638/http://variety.com/2016/film/news/will-smith-david-ayer-bright-suicide-squad-1201696226/ | archivedate=2016-09-29 }}</ref>。2016年4月，艾亞表示有興趣拍攝R級的續集<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.mtv.com/news/2868007/suicide-squad-sequel-r-rating/|title=Suicide Squad Director David Ayer Wants to Make an R-Rated Sequel Happen|publisher=MTV|last=Bell|first=Crystal|date=2016-04-14|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160723185327/http://www.mtv.com/news/2868007/suicide-squad-sequel-r-rating/|archivedate=2016-07-23}}</ref>。2017年2月，據報導，華納兄弟有著一份續集的導演候選名單，其中包括[[梅爾·吉勃遜|梅爾·吉勃遜]]<ref>{{cite web | url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/heat-vision/warner-bros-courts-mel-gibson-suicide-squad-sequel-974436 | title=Warner Bros. Courts Mel Gibson to Direct 'Suicide Squad' Sequel | publisher=''[[The_Hollywood_Reporter|The Hollywood Reporter]]'' | date=2017-02-16 | accessdate=2017-02-16 | last=Kit | first=Borys | deadurl=no | archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170216004136/http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/heat-vision/warner-bros-courts-mel-gibson-suicide-squad-sequel-974436 | archivedate=2017-02-16 }}</ref><ref>{{cite web | url=http://variety.com/2017/film/news/suicide-squad-2-director-mel-gibson-jonathan-levine-ruben-fleischer-1201989606/ | title=Mel Gibson, Jonathan Levine and Ruben Fleischer Among Directors Being Considered for ‘Suicide Squad 2’ | publisher=''[[Variety_(magazine)|Variety]]'' | date=2017-02-16 | accessdate=2017-02-16 | last=Kroll | first=Justin | deadurl=no | archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170216005944/http://variety.com/2017/film/news/suicide-squad-2-director-mel-gibson-jonathan-levine-ruben-fleischer-1201989606/ | archivedate=2017-02-16 }}</ref>。2017年3月，吉勃遜證實自己確實有與華納兄弟碰面會談。7月，[[豪梅·寇勒特-瑟拉|豪梅·寇勒特-瑟拉]]被視為片商的第一導演人選，而吉勃遜因檔期的問題退出競選，《自殺突擊隊》的續集計劃於2018年開始製作；同時，編劇[[塞克·潘|塞克·潘]]則被聘來撰寫一份新的劇本<ref>{{cite web|last=Kit|first=Borys|url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/heat-vision/suicide-squad-2-shallows-director-frontrunner-direct-1020207|title='Suicide Squad 2': 'The Shallows' Helmer Frontrunner to Direct|date=2017-07-11|accessdate=2017-07-11|work=The Hollywood Reporter|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170713050426/http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/heat-vision/suicide-squad-2-shallows-director-frontrunner-direct-1020207|archivedate=2017-07-13}}</ref>。 2017年9月，華納宣布敲定[[蓋文·歐唐納|蓋文·歐唐納]]編劇、指導。

2019年3月，蓋文·歐唐納宣布退出，随后华纳正式确认续集将由[[詹姆斯·古恩|詹姆斯·古恩]]负责接下后续指导。但就在同月，古恩对外宣布，由于第一部的口碑不佳问题，华纳已经宣布由古恩指导的《自杀小队》将完全重启。重啟版將於2021年8月6日在美國上映<ref name="ReleaseDate">{{cite web|url=https://deadline.com/2019/01/warner-bros-release-dates-galore-doctor-sleep-checks-in-this-november-the-witches-oct-2020-the-suicide-squad-returns-in-2021-1202546092/|title=Warner Bros. Release Dates Galore: 'Doctor Sleep' Checks In This November, 'The Witches' Oct. 2020; 'The Suicide Squad' Returns In 2021|website=[[Deadline_Hollywood|Deadline Hollywood]]|first=Anthony|last=D'Alessandro|date=2019-01-30|accessdate=2019-01-30|language=en-US|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190131045214/https://deadline.com/2019/01/warner-bros-release-dates-galore-doctor-sleep-checks-in-this-november-the-witches-oct-2020-the-suicide-squad-returns-in-2021-1202546092/|archive-date=2019-01-31|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

